MANKIND POSES GRAVE THREAT TO MADAGASCAR'S UNIQUE FLORA AND FAUNA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ROBERT WELLER, Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
PERINET, Madagascar 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
